text: Somatidia aranea is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by entomologist Arthur Sidney Olliff in 1889. It is known from Australia and New Zealand.BioLib.cz - Somatidia aranea. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1889
